{"id": 1462, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些影视剧形象已经过时了？", "description": "各位编剧，你们的系统得有二十年没更新过了吧。（题图来自：Alix Fizet ​​​​）", "record_count": 11225, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201701201421455bnXgUZspQB6Kl3E.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-29T17:00:56Z", "options": [{"id": 160768, "content": "男主最后为了女二死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910274}, {"id": 161536, "content": "永远没有好下场的小三", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924717}, {"id": 164096, "content": "靠运气不断打怪升级的吊儿郎当少年男主和中年男主", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714109}, {"id": 160769, "content": "1 傻白甜 傻人有傻福\n2 心机婊 心比天高 命比纸薄 倒霉的永远是身边人\n3 呆傻隐型人是Boss\n4 优秀的大师兄 永远用来衬托 好无心机的小师弟的成功 （炮灰师兄）\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922156}, {"id": 162305, "content": "傻白甜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895728}, {"id": 160770, "content": "清宫戏真的够了，我对那些长辫子不感兴趣，而且这些戏几乎都是玛丽苏，女主各种傻白甜，就算满手鲜血也是被逼的\n╮(￣⊿￣)╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922161}, {"id": 159747, "content": "放过我猴哥吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916550}, {"id": 159750, "content": "每回有困難都有男一二三四五六七捨命相救的極品歐洲人女主", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919539}, {"id": 160518, "content": "玛丽苏…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921383}, {"id": 159751, "content": "中国的电视剧该借鉴小日本了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918592}, {"id": 160007, "content": "总有妈妈半路拦截阻止  ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184381}, {"id": 160519, "content": "玛丽苏…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921383}, {"id": 159752, "content": "拉扯好几个儿女的单身母亲", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915786}, {"id": 160264, "content": "小李飞刀啊，焦恩俊该回家带孩子了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920900}, {"id": 161544, "content": "反面形象没有任何优点，正面形象又太白莲花。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924736}, {"id": 167176, "content": "绝症女主", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937694}, {"id": 159753, "content": "玛丽苏，白莲花，杰克苏，小白花，灰姑娘，恶毒女配，暖男男配，霸道总裁等等。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909804}, {"id": 165385, "content": "把反派角色包装的过分“坏”？甚至没脑，不符实际。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932898}, {"id": 159754, "content": "请宫剧。。。皇宫里得爱恨情仇", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919249}, {"id": 160010, "content": "抗日神剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808608}, {"id": 160266, "content": "手撕鬼子之流", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507236}, {"id": 163594, "content": "打架别磨叽，别在发招之前喊出招式名称好吗打的时候别哼哼哈哈好吗 蜜汁羞耻，趁对方发表感慨的时候赶快干掉他?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924443}, {"id": 160011, "content": "抗日神剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920282}, {"id": 160523, "content": "主角真能演到最后一集w(ﾟДﾟ)w", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895167}, {"id": 160012, "content": "偏见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781562}, {"id": 160268, "content": "只要努力就会成功", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915546}, {"id": 161804, "content": "傻白甜、玛丽苏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925348}, {"id": 160781, "content": "抗日剧情简单，把观众当白痴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907938}, {"id": 168717, "content": "车祸，癌症，穿越", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940869}, {"id": 159758, "content": "一點智商也沒有讓主角很好過的反派，純是為了劇情而使壞，現在哪個反派還沒有點白歷史啊?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904030}, {"id": 159759, "content": "一切狗血到脱离现实的角色都是过时，艺术源于生活，需要有演技有体验的演员", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919564}, {"id": 161039, "content": "男二的逆袭！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923060}, {"id": 160785, "content": "真爱很常见……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892547}, {"id": 159762, "content": "因为各种外部因素，打着“为了对方好”的旗号折磨对方（分手，结仇等）的一对情侣。（通常反复2-3次，男女交叉）", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919565}, {"id": 160274, "content": "巨婴人格", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920920}, {"id": 160019, "content": "抗日神剧男主←_←", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901457}, {"id": 159764, "content": "灰姑娘和王子的故事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908277}, {"id": 159765, "content": "脾气臭的男女主从没吃过瘪", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 876023}, {"id": 160277, "content": "玛丽苏，杰克苏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920921}, {"id": 159766, "content": "外面男子汉家里汉子难的战争剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760380}, {"id": 159767, "content": "各种惹事 还一脸无辜样", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883699}, {"id": 161047, "content": "龙傲天不解释", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922969}, {"id": 161303, "content": "嫉妒傻白甜女主的高知白富美女二", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923801}, {"id": 171031, "content": "失忆，傻白甜，旧梗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947423}, {"id": 160536, "content": "反派智商硬伤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915643}, {"id": 161304, "content": "敌我分明的人物关系，一看后面会反转的情节设定。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923810}, {"id": 159513, "content": "白马王子拯救灰姑娘", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919018}, {"id": 159769, "content": "把我扶上墙吧？我只是来看看的！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907543}, {"id": 159514, "content": "各种误会永远自己在心里默默承受也不和别人说，然后自己离开男主角", "image": null, "praise_count": 1110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 873551}, {"id": 159770, "content": "不相关的角色一秒就死了，可是坏人不管发生什么意外都能活到最后", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897695}]}